node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by FOOS GONE WILD on September 16, 2021 tagging @depybeatsmusic. May be an image of outdoors.

Photo by FOOS GONE WILD on September 16, 2021. May be an image of text that says '7:01 PM yo what's crackin foo, just wanted to say thank you to lil mr. e for his music, and I wanted to thank you guys for the content you post. I've had a lot of mental health problems and addictions for the past year, got sober a few months ago and my sister showed me foos gone wild after rehab. that really helped me reconnect with her and get back to center. appreciate you foos for keeping me off the skante, much love'.

node.text: THANK U FOOS FOR ALL THE POSITIVE MESSAGES 🙏🏽 #DONTSMOKESKANTE
